data.description: Priced below recent comps!! Beautiful contemporary-style home, located just 7 miles from downtown Nashville! The home features $20k in upgrades, including an exquisite designer kitchen with white quartz, high end appliances and cabinets, and loads of storage and prep space! Hardwood throughout, with large open floor plan. Level 1 houses bedroom 1 incl. full bath, along with attached 2 car garage. Level 2 features kitchen, half bath, living room and attached balcony. Walk-in closets, laundry room, bedroom 2 incl. full bath, Primary bedroom with luxury walk in shower, located on level 3. Community amenities including dog park, fire pits, gas grills and green space just steps away, local coffee shops, restaurants, and bars nearby.
